text: "But for the Grace of God" is a 2000 song by country singer Keith Urban and is the third single from his second studio album Keith Urban. It went to number 37 in the United States and topped the Billboard Hot Country Songs chart. ==References== Category:2000 songs Category:Country songs Category:Keith Urban songs Category:Music videos directed by Trey Fanjoy
